headline: DoorDash (DASH) Valuation Check As New Retail Partnerships And Regulatory Challenges Draw Attention
summary: DoorDash (DASH) is back in focus after a busy stretch that includes a new nationwide partnership with Hibbett, growing DashPass usage, severe weather disruptions, and a courtroom setback over New York City’s tipping rules.
